data.description: **VA assumable loan at 5.625%**Breathtaking 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath Azle home is ready for you to make your own! The moment you enter the grand foyer flanked by formal living room and dining room you are met with soaring ceilings, natural light, and modern elegance that is unmatchable! Custom Renewal by Anderson windows throughout. Inviting living room with wood burning fireplace and back patio access. The enviable kitchen offers built-in stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar with seating and storage, ample prep space, and bright breakfast nook with skylights. Serene primary bedroom with ensuite bath boasts dual sinks, separate shower, soaking tub, and walk-in closet. Spacious secondary bedrooms and bath. The fourth bedroom can easily be used as a comfortable home office. You and your guest will appreciate the private backyard with a large covered patio, fenced pool, gas grill, detached workshop, and mature trees Don't miss the boat and RV storage!
